(38, 21, 'en', 'Sustainability Framework', 'sustainability-framework', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/WhatsApp Image 2020-07-23 at 15.26.58.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b27d8d4d-7fff-b5b7-45af-7cc6bd337c38\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Triputra Agro Persada Group sees the importance of collaboration with other parties to achieve common goals, especially the achievement of SDGs targets and also maintaining a balance between People, Planet and Prosperity. Therefore, we actively collaborate with companies, organizations and associations to achieve these goals.</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">People</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Indigenous and Local Communities</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In running a plantation business, Triputra Agro Persada Group always prioritizes the rights of the community, especially indigenous and local communities, by giving consent without pressure and balanced information with the principle of Free Prior Informed Consent (FPIC).</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Plasma Farmers</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[Note: for Scheme smallholder in English]</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The company has a commitment to implement the Plantation Law No. 39 of 2014 concerning Plantations, especially Article 58 regarding Partnerships. This is done by carrying out the development of plasma oil palm plantations for the communities around the company concessions which are our fostered partners. This is also our commitment to the welfare of the community around our company.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Planet</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We are committed to developing sustainable and environmentally friendly palm oil plantation practices. This is done with a prudent, systematic and integrated approach with the aim of preserving environmental functions and preventing environmental pollution and / or damages which includes Protection of High Conservation Value Areas and High Carbon Stocks, Waste Management and Greenhouse Gas Mitigation.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Conservation programs that we have carried out are: Identification of High Conservation Value Areas and High Carbon Stocks, Boundary Arrangement and Safeguarding of High Conservation Value Areas, Training and awareness raising for staff and employees internally, socialization and awareness raising as well as community involvement, management and monitoring of the flora and fauna including protected species.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prosperity&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In doing business, Triputra Agro Persada Group always applies the best practices by maintaining the principle of sustainability. This is done by contributing to Energy and Food Security and long term economic viability commitments.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The company also supports a government program that encourages the use of biodiesel with a mixture of palm oil biofuels. This is because we believe that Indonesia can become a major player in meeting global biodiesel demand, especially in the long term. It is also believed to be able to help reduce the problem of current domestic energy use.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We also support the government in promoting national food security. This can be done in collaboration with the government in terms of making palm oil and its derivatives as one of the sustainable solutions to meet food needs.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If the company manages palm oil plantations in a sustainable manner, it can strengthen the economy as well as social welfare. The company believes that palm oil plantations are the most efficient producer of vegetable oil, especially in building food and energy tenacity.</span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:32:12', '2020-07-30 14:38:06');
