(39, 21, 'id', 'Kerangka Keberlanjutan', 'kerangka-keberlanjutan-1', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/WhatsApp Image 2020-07-23 at 15.26.58.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-6aa13440-7fff-2a74-135e-367f690ee5f4\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Triputra Agro Persada Group melihat pentingnya kolaborasi dengan pihak lain untuk tercapainya tujuan yang diinginkan bersama, terutama pencapaian target-target SDGs dan juga terjaganya keseimbangan antara</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> People, Planet </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">dan</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Prosperity</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. Oleh karena itu, kami aktif melakukan kerjasama baik dengan perusahaan, organisasi dan asosiasi untuk mencapai tujuan tersebut.</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">People</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Masyarakat Adat dan Lokal</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Dalam menjalankan usaha perkebunan, Triputra Agro Persada Group selalu mengedepankan hak-hak masyarakat, terutama masyarakat adat dan lokal, dengan memberikan persetujuan tanpa tekanan dan informasi berimbang dengan prinsip </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Free Prior Informed Consent</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> (FPIC).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Petani Plasma</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[Note: untuk bahasa Inggrisnya Scheme smallholder]&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Perusahaan memiliki komitmen untuk melaksanakan Undang-undang Perkebunan No.39 tahun 2014 mengenai Perkebunan, terutama Pasal 58 mengenai Kemitraan. Hal ini dilakukan dengan melaksanakan pembangunan kebun kelapa sawit plasma bagi masyarakat di sekitar konsensi perusahaan yang merupakan mitra binaan kami. Ini juga merupakan komitmen kami agar dapat menyejahterakan masyarakat di sekitar perusahaan kami.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Planet</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Kami memiliki komitmen untuk mengembangkan praktik perkebunan kelapa sawit berkelanjutan dan ramah lingkungan. Hal ini dilakukan dengan pendekatan kehati-hatian, sistematis dan terpadu dengan tujuan untuk melestarikan fungsi lingkungan hidup dan mencegah terjadinya pencemaran dan/atau kerusakan lingkungan hidup yang meliputi Perlindungan Kawasan Bernilai Konservasi Tinggi dan Stok Karbon Tinggi, Pengelolaan Limbah dan Mitigasi Gas Rumah Kaca.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Program-program konservasi yang telah kami lakukan adalah: Identifikasi Kawasan Bernilai Konservasi Tinggi dan Stok Karbon Tinggi, Penataan batas dan Pengamanan areal Nilai Konservasi Tinggi, Pelatihan dan penyadartahuan kepada staff dan karyawan secara internal, sosialisasi dan penyedartahuan serta pelibatan masyarakat, pengelolaan dan pemantauan flora dan fauna termasuk didalamnya spesies dilindungi.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prosperity&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Dalam melakukan bisnis, Triputra Agro Persada Group selalu menerapkan praktik-praktik terbaik dengan menjaga prinsip keberlanjutan. Hal tersebut dilakukan dengan memberikan kontribusi terhadap </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Energy</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> dan </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Food Security</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> dan komitmen </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">long term economic viability</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Perusahaan juga mendukung program pemerintah yang mendorong penggunaan biodiesel dengan campuran biofuel minyak sawit. Hal ini dikarenakan kami percaya bahwa Indonesia dapat menjadi pemain utama dalam memenuhi permintaan biodiesel dunia, terutama untuk jangka panjang. Hal tersebut juga dipercaya dapat membantu mengurangi masalah penggunaan energi domestik saat ini.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Kami juga mendukung pemerintah dalam mendorong ketahanan pangan nasional. Hal ini dapat dilakukan dengan cara kerjasama dengan pemerintah dalam hal membuat minyak sawit dan produk turunannya sebagai salah satu solusi berkelanjutan pemenuhan kebutuhan pangan.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Jika perusahaan mengelola kebun sawit secara berkelanjutan, maka hal itu dapat memperkuat perekonomian dan kesejahteraan sosial. Perusahaan percaya bahwa perkebunan sawit merupakan penghasil minyak nabati yang paling efisien, terutama dalam membangun ketahanan pangan dan energi. </span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:32:12', '2020-07-30 14:38:06'),
(40, 22, 'en', 'Integritas Produk', 'integritas-produk-2', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">As one of the largest palm oil plantation companies in Indonesia, Triputra Agro Persada Group complies and adheres with applicable regulations both nationally and internationally. This can be seen from a number of subsidiaries that already have Indonesian Sustainable Palm Oil (ISPO) and Roundtable Sustainability on Palm Oil (RSPO) Certificates. To date we have 12 ISPO Certificates and two RSPO Certificates.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In reducing the negative impact of company activities on the environment, we always manage the environment in accordance with the applicable laws in Indonesia. Several subsidiaries have won the Company Performance Assessment Rating Program (PROPER) with Green and Blue ratings from the Ministry of Environment and from the Provincial Environmental Agency (DLH).</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We also conduct socialization related to the sustainable palm oil management to all of the supplier farmers.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Screen Shot 2020-07-20 at 16.55.57.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: justify; color: #00301e; font-family: Roboto-Regular; font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</p>', '2020-07-15 05:32:59', '2020-07-30 14:41:29'),
(41, 22, 'id', 'Integritas Produk', 'integritas-produk', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800027272727273; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sebagai salah satu perusahaan perkebunan kelapa sawit terbesar di Indonesia, Triputra Agro Persada Group patuh dan taat kepada peraturan yang berlaku baik nasional maupun internasional. Ini terlihat dari beberapa anak perusahaan yang telah memiliki Sertifikat Indonesian Sustainable Palm Oil (ISPO) dan Roundtable Sustainability on Palm Oil (RSPO). Hingga saat ini kami telah memiliki 12 Sertifikat ISPO dan dua Sertifikat RSPO.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800027272727273; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Dalam mengurangi dampak negatif kegiatan perusahan terhadap lingkungan, kami selalu mengelola lingkungan sesuai dengan perundangan yang berlaku di Indonesia. Beberapa anak perusahaan telah meraih Program Penilaian Peringkat Kinerja Perusahaan (PROPER) dengan peringkat Hijau dan Biru dari Kementerian Lingkungan Hidup dan dari Dinas Lingkungan Hidup (DLH) Provinsi.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800027272727273; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Kami juga melakukan sosialisasi terkait pengelolaan sawit yang lestari kepada seluruh petani pemasok.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800027272727273; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Screen Shot 2020-07-20 at 16.55.57.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:32:59', '2020-07-30 14:41:29'),
(42, 23, 'en', 'Tanggung Jawab Lingkungan', 'tanggung-jawab-lingkungan-2', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We recognize the importance of protecting the environment for the sustainability and continuity of the company\'s business. Therefore, we always ensure that all subsidiaries would implement and develop sustainable and environmentally friendly palm oil plantation practices based on Best Management Practices / Good Agricultural Practices by making efforts to protect and manage the environment, such as:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">a. Protection of High Conservation Values (HCV) and Biodiversity</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">b. </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">High Carbon Stock Protection (HCS)</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">c. Mitigation of Air Pollution and Greenhouse Gas Emissions</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">d. Peatlands Management in a Responsible manner</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">e. Management of water resources and use of chemical materials</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We also have a &plusmn; 600 hectare pilot project area \"Mayong Merapun Forest\" for a multifunctional Conservation Forest that focuses on the preservation of biodiversity, both flora and fauna. This conservation area is located in the Merapun District, Berau Regency, East Kalimantan. &nbsp; </span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:33:45', '2020-07-30 14:45:34'),
(43, 23, 'id', 'Tanggung Jawab Lingkungan', 'tanggung-jawab-lingkungan', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Kami menyadari akan pentingnya menjaga kelestarian lingkungan demi keberlangsungan dan keberlanjutan bisnis perusahaan. Oleh karena itu, kami selalu memastikan agar seluruh anak perusahaan untuk menerapkan dan mengembangkan praktik perkebunan kelapa sawit berkelanjutan dan ramah lingkungan berdasarkan </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Best Management Practices/ Good Agricultural Practices </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">dengan melakukan upaya-upaya perlindungan dan pengelolaan lingkungan hidup, seperti:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">a. Perlindungan Nilai Konservasi Tinggi (HCV) dan Biodiversity</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">b. Perlindungan Stok Karbon Tinggi (HCS) </span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">c. Mitigasi Polusi Udara dan Emisi Gas Rumah Kaca</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">d. Pengelolaan Lahan Gambut yang bertanggung jawab</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">e. Pengelolaan sumber daya air dan penggunaan bahan kimia</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800027272727273; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-78356fd8-7fff-31a3-fa95-8f9a7209bf57\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Kami juga memiliki </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">pilot project</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Area Hutan Konservasi Multifungsi &ldquo;Hutan Mayong Merapun&rdquo; seluas &plusmn; 600 hektar yang berfokus pada kelestarian keanekaragaman hayati, baik flora maupun fauna. Areal konservasi ini terletak di Kecamatan Merapun, Kabupaten Berau, Kalimantan Timur.</span></span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:33:45', '2020-07-30 14:45:34'),
(44, 24, 'en', 'Tanggung Jawab Sosial', 'tanggung-jawab-sosial-2', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Our Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) programs that we have done; both independently and in collaboration with several social organizations, covering various fields, namely social, educational, cultural, economic, religious, health, and infrastructure.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Desa Makmur Peduli Api&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In the year2018, the Triputra Agro Persada Group has perfected the Fire-Free Village Program and the Corporate Social Responsibility Program to become the </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Desa Makmur Peduli Api</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> (DMPA). The DMPA program is an economic empowerment program for rural communities so that they have the ability to explore and manage the natural resources they have while still paying attention to the safety and sustainability of the environment.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The aim of the Program is to empower villages around the concession through a partnership program. This is our commitment to increase the economic potential of villages in the company\'s concession area and also foster village communities in order to protect the forest and prevent forest and land fires (Karhutla).</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Screen Shot 2020-07-20 at 17.02.41.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-fa03b3c7-7fff-b400-9485-90acf635e9be\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In the year 2019, we collaborated with the Nusantara Nature Conservation Foundation (YKAN) which is a local affiliation of The Nature Conservancy (TNC), to prevent forest and land fires through community approaches as well as to improve the welfare of rural communities together with the central government, local governments, plantation companies, mining companies, and Industrial Plantation Forests.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In addition, through the developed CSR program, we also provide guidance on Good Agricultural Practices to independent palm oil farmers who are in the vicinity of the company\'s concession area. This is done so that the independent farmers can manage palm oil plantations properly and correctly so that the productivity of their palm oil crop increases.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</p>', '2020-07-15 05:34:25', '2020-07-30 14:49:17'),
(45, 24, 'id', 'Tanggung Jawab Sosial', 'tanggung-jawab-sosial', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Program-program Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) yang telah kami lakukan; baik secara mandiri maupun dengan kerjasama dengan beberapa organisasi kemasyarakatan, mencangkup berbagai bidang, yaitu bidang sosial, pendidikan, budaya, ekonomi, keagamaan, kesehatan, dan infrastruktur.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Desa Makmur Peduli Api</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Pada tahun 2018, Triputra Agro Persada Group telah menyempurnakan Program Desa Bebas Kebakaran dan Program Corporate Social Responsibility menjadi </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Desa Makmur Peduli Api (DMPA).</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Program DMPA ini merupakan program pemberdayaan ekonomi untuk masyarakat desa agar mereka memiliki kemampuan dalam menggali dan mengelola sumber daya alam yang mereka miliki dengan tetap memperhatikan keselamatan dan kelestarian lingkungan.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tujuan dari Program ini adalah untuk memberdayakan desa di sekitar konsesi melalui program kemitraan. Ini merupakan komitmen kami untuk meningkatkan potensi ekonomi desa yang berada di area konsensi perusahaan dan juga membina masyarakat desa agar menjaga hutan dan mencegah adanya Kebakaran Hutan dan Lahan (Karhutla).</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Screen Shot 2020-07-20 at 17.02.41.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Di tahun 2019, kami bekerjasama dengan Yayasan Konservasi Alam Nusantara (YKAN) yang merupakan afiliasi lokal dari The Nature Conservancy (TNC), untuk mencegah Kebakaran Hutan dan Lahan melalui pendekatan komunitas dan peningkatan kesejahteraan masyarakat desa bersama pemerintah pusat, pemerintah daerah, perusahaan perkebunan, perusahaan pertambangan, dan Perusahaan Hutan Tanam Industri.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Selain itu, melalui program CSR yang dikembangkan, kami juga memberi pembinaan </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Good Agricultural Practices </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">kepada petani sawit mandiri yang berada di sekitar area konsensi perusahaan. Hal ini dilakukan agar para petani mandiri tersebut dapat mengelola kebun sawit secara baik dan benar sehingga produktivitas tanaman sawit mereka meningkat.</span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:34:25', '2020-07-30 14:49:17'),
(46, 25, 'en', 'Sumber Daya Manusia', 'sumber-daya-manusia-2', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Human Resources is our most valuable asset. The company believes that having good human resource capacity can make a solid foundation for the company to become better. Therefore, we strive to improve quality and also provide an equal and conducive work environment for all employees.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5d9b9b9f-7fff-c075-0850-edea89e4a3fa\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The company respects and upholds the rights of all workers, including contract workers, temporary workers, foreign workers in accordance with the applicable Indonesian laws and international principles, such as the Universal Declaration of Human Rights, International Labor Organization (ILO), United Nations Guiding Principles on Business and Human Rights and Free and Fair Labor in carrying out its operations.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/DSCF6918.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"1165\" height=\"1024\" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #00301e; font-family: Roboto-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">.</span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:35:05', '2020-07-30 14:53:05'),
(47, 25, 'id', 'Sumber Daya Manusia', 'sumber-daya-manusia', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sumber Daya Manusia merupakan aset yang paling berharga bagi kami. Perusahaan percaya bahwa dengan memiliki kapasitas sumber daya manusia yang bagus dapat menjadikan dasar yang kuat untuk Perusahaan menjadi lebih baik. Oleh karena itu, kami berusaha untuk meningkatkan kualitas dan juga menyediakan lingkungan kerja yang setara dan kondusif bagi seluruh karyawan.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3ee9ea06-7fff-be18-8018-f499aff3f5b3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Perusahaan menghormati dan menjunjung tinggi hak-hak semua pekerja, termasuk pekerja kontrak, pekerja sementara, pekerja asing sesuai dengan Hukum yang berlaku di Indonesia dan juga prinsip-prinsip Internasional, seperti Universal Declaration of Human Rights, International Labor Organisation (ILO), United Nations Guiding Principles on Business and Human Rights dan Free and Fair Labor dalam menjalankan kegiatan operasinya.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/DSCF6918.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"1024\" /></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #00301e; font-family: Roboto-Regular; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">.</span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:35:05', '2020-07-30 14:53:05'),
(48, 26, 'en', 'Occupational Health and Safety', 'occupational-health-and-safety', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We are aware that as a palm oil plantation and processing company which covers a large work area can have a high safety risk for its workers. Therefore, the Company has implemented the Occupational Safety and Health Management System (SMK3) through the Triputra SHE Management System (TSMS) Guidelines to increase the effectiveness of planned, structured, measurable and integrated Safety as well as Health (K3) protection.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">As a form of policy implementation, we ensure a safe and conducive working environment for all workers, by implementing various work programs, including: Safety Patrol, Safety and Health Audit, 5K + 1S Assessment (Regularity, Neatness, Cleanliness, Sustainability, Discipline and Safety), Safety Improvement, Contractor Safety Management System, Behaviour Based Safety (BBS) and others. Through these programs, it is expected that all employees can play an active role in achieving \"Zero Accident\" in the workplace.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800027272727273; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Pin K3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Pin Safety.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2020-07-15 05:35:43', '2020-07-30 14:56:12'),
(49, 26, 'id', 'Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja', 'keselamatan-dan-kesehatan-kerja', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Kami menyadari bahwa sebagai perusahaan perkebunan dan pengolahan kelapa sawit yang mencangkup area kerja yang luas dapat memiliki resiko keselamatan yang tinggi bagi para pekerjanya. Oleh karena itu, Perusahaan menerapkan Sistem Manajemen Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja (SMK3) melalui Pedoman Triputra SHE Manajemen System (TSMS) untuk meningkatkan efektifitas perlindungan Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja (K3) yang terencana, terstruktur, terukur dan terintegrasi.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800027272727273; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-f723b2dd-7fff-9c8f-8156-1fd4d94c28a8\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sebagai bentuk pelaksanaan kebijakan, kami memastikan lingkungan kerja yang aman dan kondusif untuk seluruh pekerja, dengan menerapkan berbagai program kerja, antara lain: </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Safety Patrol</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Safety and Health Audit</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, Penilaian 5K+1S (Keteraturan, Kerapian, Kebersihan, Kelestarian, Kedisiplinan dan </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Safety</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">), </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Safety Improvement</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Contractor Safety Management System</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, BBS </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(Behaviour Based Safety)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> dan lain-lain. Melalui program-program ini diharapkan seluruh karyawan dapat berperan aktif dalam upaya mencapai </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&ldquo;Zero Accident&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> di tempat kerja.</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800027272727273; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Pin K3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Pin Safety.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2020-07-15 05:35:43', '2020-07-30 14:56:12');
INSERT INTO `content_post_translations` (`id`, `content_post_id`, `locale`, `name`, `nicename`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(50, 27, 'en', 'Karhutla Task Force', 'karhutla-task-force-1', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We have a high commitment to the management of forest and land fire prevention (Karhutla) by establishing a Forest and Land Fire Control Task Force (Satgas Karhutla) consisting of the Chairperson, Secretary, Core Team, Supporting Team, Assistance Team as well as a person responsible for any affairs. The person in charge of affairs is divided in terms of Prevention, Extinguishing, Logistics, Rescue and Evacuation.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The company routinely trains the preparedness and responsiveness of members of the Karhutla Task Force both internally and externally. Internal training by simulating fire fighting training at least 2 times a year and externally working with the Association of Climate Change for Fire and Forest Fire Control (BPPIKHL) every year. </span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c3914bf0-7fff-8c63-7538-f018f1e4ba6d\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Apel Kesiapsiagaan.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br /><br /></span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:36:21', '2020-07-30 14:58:10'),
(51, 27, 'id', 'Tim Satgas Karhutla', 'tim-satgas-karhutla-1', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Kami memiliki komitmen yang tinggi terhadap pengelolaan pencegahan kebakaran hutan dan lahan (Karhutla) dengan membentuk Satuan Tugas Pengendalian Kebakaran Hutan dan Lahan (Satgas Karhutla) yang terdiri dari Ketua, Sekretaris, Regu Inti, Regu Pendukung, Regu Perbantuan dan Penanggung Jawab Urusan. Penanggung jawab urusan dibagi dalam hal Pencegahan, Pemadaman, Logistik, Penyelamatan dan Evakuasi.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Tahoma,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Perusahaan rutin melatih kesiapsiagaan dan ketanggapan anggota Satgas Karhutla baik secara internal maupun eksternal. Pelatihan secara internal dengan cara simulasi pelatihan penanggulangan kebakaran minimal 2 kali setahun dan secara eksternal bekerja sama dengan Balai Pengendalian Perubahan Iklim dan Kebakaran Hutan dan Lahan (BPPIKHL) setiap tahun.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c3914bf0-7fff-8c63-7538-f018f1e4ba6d\"><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wooz.in/storage/photos/2/Apel Kesiapsiagaan.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br /></span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:36:21', '2020-07-30 14:58:10'),
(52, 28, 'en', 'RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT', 'research-and-development', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">To achieve the company\'s vision to be an \"Excellent Plantation for the World\", through the Research and Development Division, the company manages and optimises the best oil palm seedlings to support sustainable business.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The division is supported by five departments with the following scope of work:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">1. Agronomy Trial: covers field and laboratory researches for crop and cost improvement through fertilizer trials, pesticide trials, utilization of oil palm by-products and conducting research on science and technology on oil palm.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">2. Advisory Services: provides advice and specific recommendations for oil palm estates in order to manage the agronomy practice effective and efficiently as well as balancing the fertiliser application to obtain maximum production.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">3. Crop Protection: controls pests and diseases before its spread (early warning system) by census detection, continuously monitoring as well as conducting biological control, utilization of biological agents and testing early symptoms of Ganoderma disease by using a digital microscope.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">4. Land Management and Techno Economic: conducts and provides advice of soil/land conservation, land management, land feasibility surveys, waste management and water management.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">5. Analytic Lab Chemistry: analyses soil, leaves, fertilizer, CPO quality to herbicides</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Company will continue to develop new innovations in order to increase the individual plant production that can increase Yield, Cost and sustainable.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The Research and Development Division plans to establish a new department, namely Seed Garden and Tissue Culture (Palm Breeding Department) which will focus on creating and improving planting materials through Biotechnology. In addition, this department will also work closely with other departments in R&amp;D to develop existing plants in the field in terms of plants, land and resistance to pests and diseases.</span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:37:56', '2020-07-29 14:07:18'),
(53, 28, 'id', 'RISET & PENGEMBANGAN', 'riset-pengembangan-1', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Untuk mewujudkan visi perusahaan untuk menjadi &ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Excellent Plantation for the World</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&rdquo; maka melalui Divisi Riset dan Pengembangan, Perusahaan mengelola dan mengoptimalisasikan bibit-bibit kelapa sawit berkualitas yang dapat menunjang bisnis berkelanjutan.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Divisi ini didukung oleh lima departemen dengan lingkup kerja sebagai berikut: </span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">1. Agronomi Trial, meliputi percobaan-percobaan lapangan dan laboratorium untuk perbaikan tanaman dan biaya, melalui percobaan pemupukan, percobaan pestisida, pemanfaatan produk limbah kelapa sawit serta melakukan penelitian pada ilmu dan teknologi kelapa sawit. </span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">2. Advisory Services: memberikan bimbingan dan rekomendasi spesifik untuk kebun kelapa sawit dalam usaha untuk mengelola praktek agronomi yang efektif dan efisien dan juga aplikasi pupuk yang seimbang untuk mendapatkan produksi yang maksimal.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">3. Crop Protection: melakukan mengendalian hama dan penyakit sebelum serangan meluas (</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">early warning system</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">) dengan melakukan deteksi sensus, monitoring berkelanjutan, hingga melakukan pengendalian secara biologi, pemanfaatan agen hayati serta melakukan pengujian terhadap gejala serangan penyakit Ganoderma sejak dini dengan menggunakan </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">microscope</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> digital.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">4. Land Management dan Techno Economic: melakukan dan memberikan bimbingan konservasi tanah/lahan, pengelolaan tanah, survey kelayakan tanah, tata kelola limbah dan pengelolaan air.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt; padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">5. Analitic Lab Chemical: menganalisa tanah, daun, pupuk, mutu CPO hingga herbisida </span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Perusahaan akan terus mengembangkan inovasi baru dalam usaha untuk meningkatkan produksi tanaman secara individu yang dapat meningkatkan </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Yield, Cost</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> dan juga berkelanjutan.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Divisi Riset dan Pengembangan berencana membentuk departemen baru, yaitu Seed Garden dan Tissue Culture (Palm Breeding Department) yang akan berfokus untuk menciptakan dan meningkatkan bahan tanam melalui Biotechnology. Selain itu, bekerja sama dengan departemen lainnya akan mengembangkan tanaman di lapangan agar dapat ditinjau dari segi tanaman, lahan dan resistansi terhadap hama dan penyakit. </span></p>', '2020-07-15 05:37:56', '2020-07-29 14:07:18'),
(54, 29, 'en', 'Laboratorium', 'laboratorium-2', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">PT Triputra Agro Persada has an Analytical Chemistry laboratory that provides testing services such as leaves, soil, fertiliser, bunches samples as well as CPO quality and Chlorine in order to produce sustainable palm oil. In addition, the laboratory also gives agronomy services to other oil palm company, such as fertiliser recommendations, soil survey, aerial photography, and palm oil agronomy training.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The agronomy services will carry out comprehensive and in-depth agronomy checks and analyses in order to have the right solution for the development of the palm oil in producing optimal growth and production.</span><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-dca105d6-7fff-6a7a-b7cf-cdd1354becea\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This laboratory already has SNI ISO/IEC 17025: 2018 certification issued by the National Accreditation Committee (KAN). Besides being used by the Company and its subsidiaries, this laboratory service can be used by other plantation companies.</span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://tapadmin.wo